(13982, 202, 2, 'Article with standard configurator', '', 'The standard configurator offers the opportunity, to selct the desired constellation, without following a certain order. All groups can be selected by customers with the corresponding options.', '<p>The standard configurator offers the opportunity, to selct the desired constellation, without following a certain order. All groups can be selected by customers with the corresponding options.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
