(160, 'article', 'a:3:{s:10:"txtArtikel";s:33:"Payment methods & risk management";s:19:"txtshortdescription";s:75:"In Shopware, you have different opportunities to handle the risk management";s:19:"txtlangbeschreibung";s:268:"<p>In Shopware, you have different opportunities to handle the risk management. You can use them or other factors to define certain payment methods for certain customer groups.</p>\n<p>In this example, you are not offered the payment method "invoice" for instance".</p>";}', 228, '2'),
